        "title": "How to access all statestore data in Kstream DSL .transform() method",
        "body": "<p>Trying to access all key values in the defined statestore but, in .transform() method i can access only with one key (which is the source key)<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>KeyValueStore&lt;String, String&gt; SS=context.getStateStore(\"macs\");\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>the SS is not able to get all key values in statestore <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>SS.get(\"key1\");\nSS.get(\"key2\");\nSS.get(\"key3\");\nSS.get(\"key4\");\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>only 1 out of 4 returns values rest all returns null <\/p>\n",
